545
01:19:10.742 --> 01:19:11.940
<i>Ja...</i>

546
01:19:17.874 --> 01:19:19.534
Wat moet ik doen?

547
01:19:21.794 --> 01:19:23.205
<i>Ik weet 't niet.</i>

548
01:19:25.506 --> 01:19:28.957
't Is vreemd.
